      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. The chassis remains factory-stiff with documented subframe reinforcement, paired with an impeccably maintained Getrag 420G manual gearbox. Every bushing, link, and damper reflects a zero-compromise maintenance philosophy. The limited-slip differential operates with surgical precision, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. With a flawless paint meter reading and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning collector.",
